  <mainContent><![CDATA[<h2>Course Overview</h2>
<p>This course is designed for students who want to pursue a career in creative digital industries and develop a strong grounding in digital media production with an emphasis on creativity and innovation.</p>
<h2>Entry Requirements</h2>
<ul>
<li>You will need to have achieved one of the following:</li>
<li>Foundation Diploma in a relevant subject</li>
<li>BTEC Level 3 Extended Diploma in a relevant subject</li>
<li>A-Level at Grade C or above in a creative subject.</li>
</ul>
<p>You will also be required to present a portfolio of artwork to demonstrate your commitment and suitability for our course.</p>
<h2>What will I study? </h2>
<p>You will develop skills in visual design, games design, video production, animation, creative thinking, interface design and product development – as well as computing, digital technologies and programming. All assessment is through coursework that is submitted at specific points throughout the programme.</p>]]></mainContent>
